<BR>
Sure, I'm frustrated that some of the features promised with Luclin have not come out yet.  But companies multi-task all the time.  Your jumping to conclusions to assume that the formation of the Legends team will in any way affect our game.  If their profit had not been invested in the Legends team, it would have been invested somewhere else.  They are not going to go into dept just to provide more customer service.<BR>
